import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'

// Import global CSS via webpack so dev-server serves them with correct MIME types
import '@/assets/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import '@/assets/css/assets/slick.min.css'
import '@/assets/css/assets/fakeloader.css'
import '@/assets/css/icofont.min.css'
import '@/assets/css/assets/jquery-ui.min.css'
import '@/assets/css/assets/jquery.fancybox.css'
import '@/assets/css/assets/nice-select.css'
import '@/assets/css/assets/animate.min.css'
import '@/assets/css/assets/meanmenu.min.css'
import '@/assets/css/assets/plyr.min.css'
import '@/assets/css/assets/animate-headline.css'
import '@/assets/css/assets/plugin.css'

import '@/assets/css/default.css'
import '@/assets/style.css'
import '@/assets/css/responsive.css'

createApp(App).mount('#app')
